message.raw:
Implemented drag/drop into queuemanager

Also implemented "delete" key to delete selected items from queue manager
Fixed a bug where the new_rep_name function hadn't been moved across to the QueueManager class
Fixed a bug where the process_request function was not using the correct logger variable
